{"tid":2215830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"恆香假月餅疑雲 海關原來拉錯人 問題在一個「老」字","createTime":"2020-09-24T08:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:13:40.000Z","uid":235152,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91725d32b1aeaa74386c4a59f1c21bf44f12f86d","tid":2215830,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）海關上週接報後在元朗檢走一批在內地生產冒牌恆香月餅和餅券，並拘捕被指是集團主腦的鄭鴻杰。77歲的鄭鴻杰下午以「恆香餅家」股東身份，在元朗大樹下西路的恒香餅家工場見記者，澄清該批月餅由有百年歷史的「恆香餅家」所生產，強調是正貨。<br />\n<br />\n鄭鴻杰強調，自己同為「恆香老餅家」的股東持有人，絕不會作出抄襲之舉。他指出，「恆香老餅家」一直就股權開展訴訟多年，稱相信有利益衝突人士向海關提供誤導資料，導致月餅被清走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077618&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=bb3532a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077618&h=0539f5eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077618</a>"},{"pid":"b925be0926752d4450671ee37fc2fb9cbcdb620b","tid":2215830,"uid":276273,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"我有一手匯豐，係咪可以印銀紙，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350d75bad54c6400d367fc8a1faa606e76c67e94","tid":2215830,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"點解有人係香港賣左咁多年正版喬丹牌波鞋<br />\n海關都唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90a02597346f67976973fa9d867ade776ffbb1d","tid":2215830,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b925be0926752d4450671ee37fc2fb9cbcdb620b","tid":2215830,"uid":276273,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"我有一手匯豐，係咪可以印銀紙，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020